=== 安全问题 ===
尽管主办方承诺会加强安保，但里约仍然存在许多安全问题，2016年1月到5月就有2036起谋杀案。2016年5月21日，西班牙代表团三名成员在里约圣特雷莎被五名年轻人持枪抢劫，其中两人手持手枪<ref>{{cite news |date=2016-05-21 |title=3 members of Spanish sailing team robbed at gunpoint in Rio |url=https://swimswam.com/3-members-of-spanish-sailing-team-robbed-at-gunpoint-in-rio/ |newspaper=SwimSwam |access-date=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523112219/https://swimswam.com/3-members-of-spanish-sailing-team-robbed-at-gunpoint-in-rio/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年6月，市长的一名保安下班时被抢后遇害；一名医生在高速公路上被杀；澳大利亚残奥代表人也遭到持枪枪击<ref name="latimes 20160630"/><ref name="Licon 2016">{{cite web | last=Licon | first=Adriana Gomez | title=Clashes rage in Rio as police try to capture drug trafficker | website=The Big Story | date=2016-06-29 | url=http://www.bigstory.ap.org/article/27c15bd608de4ecc868e8be4922b8d56/clashes-rage-rio-police-try-capture-drug-trafficker | accessdate=2016-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630222457/http://www.bigstory.ap.org/article/27c15bd608de4ecc868e8be4922b8d56/clashes-rage-rio-police-try-capture-drug-trafficker | archive-date=2016-06-30 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="Licon 2016"/>。奥运场馆主要道路红线上一名枪手用枪指着来往车辆的图片被爆出<ref>{{cite web | author=Matt Roper | title=Shooter aims on Rio's terror road to strike terror in Olympics fans | website=Mail Online | date=2016-06-21 | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3646384/Rio-s-highway-terror-Shooter-takes-aim-cars-Red-Line-road-Olympic-athletes-fans-travel-games-Brazil.html | accessdate=2016-06-30 | archive-date=2016-06-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622143343/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3646384/Rio-s-highway-terror-Shooter-takes-aim-cars-Red-Line-road-Olympic-athletes-fans-travel-games-Brazil.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>；黑帮在火线火并据称司空见惯，已造成多人死亡，其中一名17岁女孩于5月遇害<ref>{{cite web | title=Teen death sparks concerns over Rio Olympics safety | website=The New Daily | date=2016-05-11 | url=http://thenewdaily.com.au/sport/2016/05/11/brazil-olympics-safety/ | accessdate=2016-06-30 | archive-date=2019-09-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912093226/https://thenewdaily.com.au/sport/other-sports/2016/05/11/brazil-olympics-safety/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Markowitz 2016">{{cite web | last=Markowitz | first=Eric | title=Road to Rio: As Crime Explodes In Rio, Private Security Forces Step In As Protectors | website=International Business Times | date=2016-05-31 | url=http://www.ibtimes.com/road-rio-crime-explodes-rio-private-security-forces-step-protectors-2365180 | accessdate=2016-06-30 | archive-date=2016-06-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603180500/http://www.ibtimes.com/road-rio-crime-explodes-rio-private-security-forces-step-protectors-2365180 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。女孩被谋杀及其他案件促使一些国家考虑将私人保安团队带到奥运会<ref name="Markowitz 2016"/>。

2016年6月30日，[[科帕卡瓦纳_(里约热内卢)|科帕卡瓦纳]]奥运沙滩排球场附近的警方在海滩上发现一只脚和其他残肢，可能出自一位已经遇害的“女性或青少年”<ref name="latimes 20160630">{{cite web | title=Human body parts found near beach volleyball site for Olympics in Rio | website=latimes.com | date=2016-06-30 | url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/la-sp-oly-rio-2016-human-body-parts-found-near-olympics-1467297917-htmlstory.html | accessdate=2016-06-30 | archive-date=2016-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630155304/http://www.latimes.com/sports/la-sp-oly-rio-2016-human-body-parts-found-near-olympics-1467297917-htmlstory.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。警方表示残肢被海水冲干净，引发对里约暴力事件的潜在担忧<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/rio-2016/2016/06/29/beach-volleyball-body-parts/86539174/ |title=Body parts washed up on Rio Shore |date=2016-06-30 |website=USA today |access-date=2016-06-30 |archive-date=2016-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630034918/http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/rio-2016/2016/06/29/beach-volleyball-body-parts/86539174/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Licon 2016"/>。

