==== 美国4×100米接力问题 ====
8月18日在田径女子4×100米接力的第二组预赛中，美国队[[愛麗森·費利克斯|愛麗森·費利克斯]]即将向[[英格利希·加德納|英格利希·加德納]]交接棒时，費利克斯摔倒，接力棒掉落。美国队成绩因此受到影响。美国队称在交接棒中受到巴西队的阻挡，提出申诉。仲裁认为美国队员确实受巴西队员阻挡影响成绩，批准这一申诉，取消了巴西队的成绩，美国队则被允许单独重赛一次。[[国际田联|国际田联]]要求美国队在单独重赛时使用相同的队员和棒次顺序，在相同的赛道上进行。此前排名第八晋级决赛的中国队对此提出抗议，但抗议被驳回。美国队在单独重赛后以排名第一的身份进入决赛，中国队则因此失去晋级资格。中国认为此判决有失公允，再次提出申诉，建议九支队伍参加决赛，决赛分为两组进行，但此次申诉也同样被驳回。<ref>{{cite web|title=US women through to 4x100m relay final after Olympic scare|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/08/18/sport/us-women-4x100-to-re-run-race/index.html|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2016-08-19|date=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818215924/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/08/18/sport/us-women-4x100-to-re-run-race/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=USA will have chance to rerun women's 4x100m after dropping baton|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/18/usa-4x100m-relay-team-dropped-baton-rerun|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-08-19|date=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818201916/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/18/usa-4x100m-relay-team-dropped-baton-rerun|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=中国田径队就“美国队重赛”二次申诉再遭驳回|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/sports/2016-08/19/c_129242044.htm|publisher=新华社|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822121415/http://news.xinhuanet.com/sports/2016-08/19/c_129242044.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>中国田径队认为此判决不够公平，指出肢体碰撞在田径比赛中很常见，巴西队员无意影响美国队员，此前类似事件的判决多是不再重赛；中方还认为美国队交接棒中本身即存在失误，掉棒并非完全是巴西队员阻挡所致，不应将失误原因全部归咎于阻挡；中方在申诉中提出“单独重赛”无干扰、无竞争，与正常竞赛的环境不同，因此不够公平，但中国田径队依然称“尊重国际田联做出的最后裁决”。<ref>{{cite web|title=中国田径队：我们据理力争 结果有失公允|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/sports/2016-08/19/c_1119416817.htm|publisher=新华社|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823004754/http://news.xinhuanet.com/sports/2016-08/19/c_1119416817.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>这是奥运会田径比赛中首次出现“单独重赛”，<ref>{{cite web|title=Relay rerun: Bobble leads to strange day for US women|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/olympics/a-bobble-leads-to-a-rerun-on-another-crazy-day-for-us-relays/2016/08/18/367a85a6-6567-11e6-b4d8-33e931b5a26d_story.html|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160819075652/https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/olympics/a-bobble-leads-to-a-rerun-on-another-crazy-day-for-us-relays/2016/08/18/367a85a6-6567-11e6-b4d8-33e931b5a26d_story.html}}</ref>但在2014年[[欧洲田径锦标赛|欧洲田径锦标赛]]中曾出现类似的“单独重赛”判决。<ref>{{cite web|title=22nd European Athletics Championships - Day Five|url=http://www.gettyimages.com.au/event/22nd-european-athletics-championships-day-five-505612807#bjorn-blauwhof-of-the-netherlands-starts-a-rerun-of-the-mens-4x400m-picture-id453693924|publisher=Getty Images|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827013712/http://www.gettyimages.com.au/event/22nd-european-athletics-championships-day-five-505612807#bjorn-blauwhof-of-the-netherlands-starts-a-rerun-of-the-mens-4x400m-picture-id453693924|dead-url=no}}</ref>

