lympics 2016: Bulgarian Silvia Danekova fails drugs test|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/37055298|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915035555/http://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/37055298|dead-url=no}}</ref>吉尔吉斯斯坦举重运动员{{le|伊扎特·阿爾特科夫|Izzat Artykov}}在男子举重69公斤级的比赛中获得铜牌，但在之后的药检中检出[[番木鳖碱|番木鳖碱]]阳性，其铜牌被取消。之前获得的第四名的哥伦比亚选手{{le|路易斯·哈維爾·莫斯克拉·洛薩諾|Luis Javier Mosquera}}因此上升至第三名，获得铜牌。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rio Olympics 2016: Izzat Artykov stripped of weightlifting bronze|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/37122892|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219225902/http://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/37122892|dead-url=no}}</ref>摩尔多瓦皮划艇选手{{le|謝爾蓋·塔爾諾夫斯基|Serghei Tarnovschi}}因药检不过关被临时禁赛，无法参加男子1000公尺雙人加拿大式艇的比赛。<ref>{{cite web|title=Canoe bronze medalist suspended 'after failed drug test'|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-rio-doping-canoeing-idUSKCN10T219|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819192613/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-rio-doping-canoeing-idUSKCN10T219|dead-url=no}}</ref>

