==== 霍爾頓-孫楊之爭 ====
[[麥克·霍爾頓|麥克·霍爾頓]]贏得[[里约奥运会|里约奥运会]]400米自由泳金牌，在賽後媒體採訪時，表示自己「只是打敗了吃禁藥的對手」，还称在比赛中获得亚军的中國選手[[孙杨|孙杨]]为“服[[体育禁药|药]]的骗子”。他称自己并非针对孙杨，只是对药检阳性的运动员不满。之後麥克再度受訪時表示，「孙杨藥檢曾被驗出使用禁藥是事實」、「運動界對於禁藥應該採取零容忍政策」<ref>{{cite web|title='Sun Yang is just the drug cheat': Aussie Mack Horton slams Chinese rival after getting the ultimate revenge and beating him to win Rio gold... and urges other athletes to 'name and shame' dopers|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3727368/Rio-Olympics-Mack-Horton-calls-Sun-Yang-drug-cheat-ahead-400m-final.html|date=2016-08-06|accessdate=2016-08-06|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806232538/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3727368/Rio-Olympics-Mack-Horton-calls-Sun-Yang-drug-cheat-ahead-400m-final.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但他也承认，他使用极具挑衅性的“骗子”来称呼对手孙杨，是由於他在賽前長期採取的策略，在心理上刻意貶低對手而舒緩自身的壓力，才會在賽後訪問將貶低對手的言語脫口而出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/sport/olympics/rio-2016/olympics-swimming/mack-hortons-stirring-gold-medal-win-a-mental-sting-as-well-as-a-physical-triumph-20160807-gqmskm.html|title=Rio Olympics 2016: Mack Horton's stirring gold medal win a mental sting as well as a physical triumph|publisher=Sydney Morning Herald|author=Phil Lutton|accessdate=2016-08-09|date=2016-08-07|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808140154/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/olympics/rio-2016/olympics-swimming/mack-hortons-stirring-gold-medal-win-a-mental-sting-as-well-as-a-physical-triumph-20160807-gqmskm.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/07/mack-horton-and-relay-team-get-australia-off-to-golden-start-in-rio-pool|title=Mack Horton and relay team get Australia off to golden start in Rio pool|work=The Guardian|date=2016-08-07|accessdate=2016-08-09|archive-date=2016-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807033659/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/07/mack-horton-and-relay-team-get-australia-off-to-golden-start-in-rio-pool|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

孫楊對此則回應：「这是澳大利亚人的小伎俩，每一位能够来到奥运会的选手都应该受到尊重。」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/others/swim/2016-08-07/doc-ifxutfpc4694142.shtml |title=孙杨回击霍顿：澳洲小伎俩 每个选手都值得尊重 |accessdate=2016-08-14 |archive-date=2016-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821121205/http://sports.sina.com.cn/others/swim/2016-08-07/doc-ifxutfpc4694142.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>中国游泳协会认为霍尔顿此番言论「缺乏素养和体育道德」，要求澳大利亚游泳协会对此事道歉，但遭到澳大利亞方面的拒絕。<ref name=Guardian/>

