== 倒票醜聞 ==
8月5日，里约警方逮捕了两名涉嫌将数百张分配给爱尔兰奥委会的门票转售的人士。其中一人受雇于2012年爱尔兰奥委会授权的门票经销商THG Sports，但爱尔兰否认涉事。该国体育部长谢恩·罗斯（{{lang|en|Shane Ross}}）下令“彻查”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/news/politics/ross-to-carry-out-robust-inquiry-into-olympic-tickets-1.2754010|title=Ross to carry out ‘robust inquiry’ into Olympic tickets|last=Clarke|first=Vivienne|date=2016-08-12|work=The Irish Times|accessdate=2016-08-12|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813141341/http://www.irishtimes.com/news/politics/ross-to-carry-out-robust-inquiry-into-olympic-tickets-1.2754010|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.ie/sport/rio-2016-olympics/face-of-irish-executive-arrested-over-alleged-sale-of-3m-official-tickets-at-rio-olympics-34950406.html|title=Face of Irish executive arrested over alleged sale of €3m official tickets at Rio Olympics -|last=Sandy|first=Matt|date=2016-08-09|work=Irish Independent|accessdate=2016-08-12|archive-date=2016-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819031744/http://www.independent.ie/sport/rio-2016-olympics/face-of-irish-executive-arrested-over-alleged-sale-of-3m-official-tickets-at-rio-olympics-34950406.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而本届的门票经销商Pro 10 Sports Management表示被捕男子负责为单位分发合法购买的门票<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2016/0812/808666-olympics-tickets-rio-2016/|title=Pro 10: Mallon distributing tickets on its behalf|date=2016-08-12|work=RTÉ.ie|accessdate=2016-08-12|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813134900/http://www.rte.ie/news/2016/0812/808666-olympics-tickets-rio-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月17日，爱尔兰奥委会主席{{le|帕特·希基|Pat Hickey (sports administrator)}}在里约被警方带走调查<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.ie/sport/rio-2016-olympics/president-of-olympic-council-of-ireland-pat-hickey-taken-to-hospital-following-arrest-34973224.html|title=President of Olympic Council of Ireland Pat Hickey 'taken to hospital' following arrest|last=Doyle|first=Kevin|date=2016-08-17|work=Irish Independent|accessdate=2016-08-17|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022160736/http://www.independent.ie/sport/rio-2016-olympics/president-of-olympic-council-of-ireland-pat-hickey-taken-to-hospital-following-arrest-34973224.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至8月22日，3名爱尔兰奥委会官员基尔提（Kevin Kilty）、海尼汉（Dermot Henihan）及马丁（Stephen Martin）被控涉及里约奥运会非法倒票，其护照被警方暂扣并接受调查，手机与电脑也被查封。爱尔兰奥委会主席希基现关押于班古重刑监狱，之後交保但限制出境以等候法院的听审<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.sohu.com/20160822/n465419038.shtml|title=爱尔兰奥委会主席涉高价倒票 被禁里约重刑监狱|date=2016-08-22|work=人民网|accessdate=2016-08-22|archive-date=2016-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913042618/http://news.sohu.com/20160822/n465419038.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

